COMPANY_DESCRIPTION:
Lighthouse Realty is a family owned and operated full service real estate company.  We understand how important the purchase or sale of your home is to your family. In fact, our own experience with buying and selling a home is one of the reasons we developed MyWay Home Selling Services. 
 
Our passion is bringing clarity to the purchase or sale of your home, in a way that lets you keep more of your hard-earned money. You know exactly what you are paying and what services you are receiving. There are no surprises.
 
Our commitment is to offer professional real estate services that are focused on your needs, and that reflect the true cost of buying or selling your home
